09:14.305 --> 09:16.223
♪ In trouble town ♪

09:17.558 --> 09:19.226
♪ Oh ♪

09:20.394 --> 09:22.146
♪ Yeah ♪

09:23.064 --> 09:24.815
- ♪ You wreck me, baby... ♪
- Stop the case!

09:25.775 --> 09:28.235
♪ Yeah, you break me in two ♪

09:28.652 --> 09:30.863
